effects.msn_description: Fighting Awakened Kojima from Kojima Return Event Ninja Sage / Ninja Saga!
msn_dialog: Shin-Left:You are [character_name], right? I am the tutor of this Academy, Shin. Defeat the training dummy and show me what you got.

effects.msn_description: Fighting 3 Hollows from Bleach Series! Source : Ninja Sage
msn_dialog: Kenta-Left:Hi [character name]! I am Kenta, the famous ninja blacksmith of Fire Village.
Kenta-Left:I have a mission for you.
Kenta-Left: My weapon was stolen. Could you get it back for me?

effects.msn_description: Fighting Taowu from S6 Anniversary Ninja Saga!
msn_dialog: Yudai-Left:Deliver the confidential letter to the Black Ops centre outside the village. Enemies may attack you. Be careful!

effects.msn_description: Fighting Tengu Goblin from S9 Anniversary Ninja Saga!
msn_dialog: Mai-Left:Hi [character name]! I am Mai! I used to be a ninja just like you, but I decided to carry on with our family business. Weaving ninja cloths has been a tradition in our family.
Mai-Left:Yesterday, a group of female ninja stole the Golden Silk from my home. It is the most expensive silk! Can you take it back for me?

effects.msn_description: Fighting Chika from S8 Anniversary Ninja Saga / S2 Anniversary Ninja Sage!
msn_dialog: Shin-Left:Recently our conflict with the samurai has intensified! A few samurai just broke into the village and created disturbances! Dispatch them, quick!

effects.msn_description: Deliver Michi's medical supplies to the neighboring town.
msn_dialog: Michi-Left:Hi [character_name]! I am Michi, the head nurse of the village.
Michi-Left:Please help us to deliver some medical supplies to the neighboring town. They are suffering from a shortage.

effects.msn_description: Deliver some Sweet Dangos.
msn_dialog: Yuna-Left:[Character_name], I am Yuna, I make delicious Dango and Onigiri. I am also good at making ramen. If ramen is your thing, maybe you should try mine.
Yuna-Left:There is a festival in the neighbouring town. Can you deliver these dangos to my dad? He is in the festival.

effects.msn_description: Fighting Jurojin from S6 Anniversary Ninja Saga / S1 Anniversary Ninja Legends!
msn_dialog: BlackOpsUnit-Left:We were just seized outside the village... some of us are poisoned by their weapons... Get us the antidote! Go!

effects.msn_description: Fighting Ebisu from S6 Anniversary Ninja Saga / S1 Anniversary Ninja Legends!
msn_dialog: Chiyo-Left:Hello, can you help me buy a Pearl Kunai for Aiko? It is her birthday tomorrow.

effects.msn_description: Save the White Monk's temple from the Wandering Monks.
msn_dialog: Genzu-Left:I have a mission for you. The White Monks have come to us for help. The Wandering Monks have been disturbing their temple.

effects.msn_description: Protect the Merchant Ships
msn_dialog: Yudai-Left:A group of Ninja Pirates are attacking the Merchant ships now! Some ninjas have already been there fighting the Pirates. Go there and assist them!

effects.msn_description: The mining field is occupied, go and get it back !

Someone robbed Kusuma's valuables, you must go and help him to get them back!
There are many Soil Ninja working on something in the forest, go and investigate them!
Kusuma needs help again, ask him and find out what you can do.

Kaiza heard a rumor about the legendary weapon, he is asking you to come with him. Is this a trap?
